  <p>
    Launch time: <span id='label_launch'> </span><br>
    Elapsed time: <span id='label_elapsed'> </span><br>
    Legend: job wall time / memory usage (RAM) <span id='label_legend'> </span>
  </p>
  <div id="timeline"></div>
</div>

